data.description:
Beautiful 5 bedroom 4.5 bath house with beautiful pool located in El Dorado Hills. The home features a family room, a dining room and a separate open kitchen with a living room with 2 fireplaces. 

Full size Washer and Dryer included. 

Quiet neighborhood close to restaurants, grocery stores and quick access to the freeway. 5 minutes to Town Center.

Utilities 
Tenant is responsible for gas & electric and water. First month of Rent+ Deposit due at lease signing. 

Pet Policy
Small dogs are considered with an additional deposit. NO CATS.

Credit and Income Qualifications 
Must have excellent credit, monthly income must equal 2.5x the rent and references will be checked. 

Lease Terms
3, 6 or 12 month lease options are available. 
Month to month lease option available with a higher deposit.
